data.description: Welcome to 5207 Rutland Court. This SE Cape stunner has been completely reimagined into one of the nicest properties available in the area today. Offering 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a 1 car garage, and a bright & open floor plan, this home lives very comfortably. Upgrades completed in 2023 include a brand new 24 gauge metal roof, luxury vinyl flooring throughout, solid wood soft close cabinets, granite countertops, GE stainless steel appliances, a water heater, stunning bathroom tile work and glass shower enclosures, light fixtures/fans throughout, all new interior doors & trim, complete interior and exterior paint, and so much more. Other upgrades include a new AC unit (2020) and a hurricane impact & insulated garage door (2020). Situated on a beautiful lot with plenty of room for a pool, you'll enjoy the outdoor space this home has to offer. Located close to so many local hot spots including the Cape Coral Yacht Club, Downtown Cape Coral, Downtown Fort Myers, and so much more you'll enjoy the convenient lifestyle this location affords you. With an opportunity to become the perfect vacation rental or part time residence, this home is ready for season. Act fast, this one won't last!
